OL,3,CVigil held in honour of murdered baby
OL,4,CPreston Davey on what would have
OL,6,FScores of people have gathered for an
OL,7,Femotional candlelight vigil in memory
OL,8,Fof a 13-month-old who was murdered by
OL,9,Fhis adoptive father.
OL,11,FThe memorial for Preston Davey took
OL,12,Fplace at the Preston Flag Market on
OL,13,FJune 16th, marking what would have
OL,14,Fbeen the little boy's fourth birthday.
OL,16,FFamilies and other members of the
OL,17,Fpublic were seen in tears after
OL,18,Flighting candles and leaving teddies
OL,19,Fto remember the toddler.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
