OL,3,CVigil held in honour of murdered baby
OL,4,CPreston Davey on what would have
OL,6,FBubbles were released into the air as
OL,7,Fa bagpiper played Amazing Grace to the
OL,8,Fcrowd.
OL,10,FOrganiser Niamh Clarke told ITV
OL,11,FGranada Reports, "When I first came
OL,12,Facross this case it really did touch
OL,13,Fme and reduce me to tears.
OL,15,F"Sometimes ignorance is bliss. I just
OL,16,Fcouldn't get him off my mind and felt
OL,17,Fcompelled to do something for him."
