OL,3,CVigil held in honour of murdered baby
OL,4,CPreston Davey on what would have
OL,6,FA trial at Preston Crown Court
OL,7,Frevealed the abuse Preston suffered at
OL,8,Fthe hands of Jamie Varley, 37, and his
OL,9,Fpartner, John McGowan-Fazakerley, 32.
OL,11,FA jury heard how Preston was routinely
OL,12,Fill-treated, physically assaulted, and
OL,13,Fsexually abused while in their care
OL,14,Ffor just under four months at their
OL,15,Fhome in Blackpool.
OL,17,FThe court was told the toddler had
OL,18,Fsuffered 40 traumatic injuries before
OL,19,Fhis death on 27 July 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
