OL,3,CVigil held in honour of murdered baby
OL,4,CPreston Davey on what would have
OL,6,FFollowing the seven-week trial,
OL,7,Fmembers of the jury spent around 14
OL,8,Fhours considering the verdicts.
OL,10,FJamie Varley was found guilty of
OL,11,Fmurder, two counts of assault by
OL,12,Fpenetration, five counts of cruelty to
OL,13,Fa child, grievous bodily harm, sexual
OL,14,Fassault of a child, and 13 counts of
OL,15,Ftaking indecent photos or videos of a
OL,16,Fchild. He was also convicted of making
OL,17,Fand distributing indecent images.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
